Title: Fixed point analysis of a scalar theory with an external field

Authors: A.Bonanno and D.Zappala'

Comments: 4 pages, LaTex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D56 (1997) 3759-3762

A momentum dependent projection of the Wegner-Hougton equation is derived fora scalar theory coupled to an external field. This formalism is useful todiscuss the phase diagram of the theory. In particular we study some propertiesof the Gaussian fixed point.